                        <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/05/mi6-ghost-money.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a> &#8195;| &#8195;<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/privacy">Why no sharings links?</a><br>
												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/accountability" title="View all posts in Accountability" rel="category tag">Accountability</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/afghanistan" title="View all posts in Afghanistan" rel="category tag">Afghanistan</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/articles" title="View all posts in Articles" rel="category tag">Articles</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/cia" title="View all posts in CIA" rel="category tag">CIA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/drones-2" title="View all posts in Drones" rel="category tag">Drones</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/drugs-2" title="View all posts in Drugs" rel="category tag">Drugs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/economics" title="View all posts in Economics" rel="category tag">Economics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/gaddafi" title="View all posts in Gaddafi" rel="category tag">Gaddafi</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/intelligence" title="View all posts in Intelligence" rel="category tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/law" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/leap" title="View all posts in LEAP" rel="category tag">LEAP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/libya" title="View all posts in Libya" rel="category tag">Libya</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/mi6" title="View all posts in MI6" rel="category tag">MI6</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/national-security" title="View all posts in National security" rel="category tag">National security</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/politics" title="View all posts in Politics" rel="category tag">Politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/rttv" title="View all posts in RTTV" rel="category tag">RTTV</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/syria" title="View all posts in Syria" rel="category tag">Syria</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/terrorism" title="View all posts in Terrorism" rel="category tag">Terrorism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/un" title="View all posts in UN" rel="category tag">UN</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/war-2" title="View all posts in War" rel="category tag">War</a>			</span>
