				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/cia" rel="tag">CIA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/fbi" rel="tag">FBI</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/sibel-edmonds" rel="tag">Sibel Edmonds</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/valerie-plame" rel="tag">Valerie Plame</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblower" rel="tag">whistleblower</a>			</span>
						
